632
00:34:33,840 --> 00:34:35,320
you can't abandon me.

633
00:34:40,760 --> 00:34:42,550
The Fallen Deity under the Lava is awakening.

634
00:34:43,920 --> 00:34:45,190
I don't know if what he said

635
00:34:46,070 --> 00:34:46,960
is true or false.

636
00:34:50,440 --> 00:34:51,280
Regardless,

637
00:34:52,110 --> 00:34:52,760
Xie Xuechen,

638
00:34:54,000 --> 00:34:54,590
you must know...

639
00:34:56,760 --> 00:34:57,880
that whether it's Big Brother

640
00:34:58,710 --> 00:34:59,840
or that Fallen Deity,

641
00:35:00,630 --> 00:35:01,630
neither of them is you.

642
00:35:02,670 --> 00:35:03,400
In my heart,

643
00:35:04,230 --> 00:35:06,320
you're not anyone's shadow or substitute.

644
00:35:07,590 --> 00:35:09,110
You're the one and only Xie Xuechen...

645
00:35:14,840 --> 00:35:15,760
and my Xie Xuechen.

646
00:35:26,110 --> 00:35:26,920
It seems

647
00:35:28,070 --> 00:35:29,150
like the situation is temporarily resolved,

648
00:35:30,280 --> 00:35:31,400
but the problem remains.

649
00:35:37,150 --> 00:35:38,800
The seal on the Dark Abyss is only temporary.

650
00:35:40,840 --> 00:35:41,920
As long as the inner demons persist,

651
00:35:42,920 --> 00:35:44,960
it's only a matter of time before the Dark Clan breaks free.

652
00:35:45,510 --> 00:35:46,400
And He Xianwo...

653
00:35:47,550 --> 00:35:48,550
No one knows his intention

654
00:35:49,070 --> 00:35:49,800
or he's whereabouts.

655
00:35:50,510 --> 00:35:51,480
He's plotted for years.

656
00:35:52,630 --> 00:35:53,710
He must have a purpose.

657
00:35:54,440 --> 00:35:55,400
There's no way

658
00:35:55,510 --> 00:35:56,550
