659
00:35:57,880 --> 00:35:58,480
Mr. Xie!

660
00:36:01,400 --> 00:36:02,440
Why are you in such a rush?

661
00:36:03,070 --> 00:36:03,670
What's happened?

662
00:36:04,280 --> 00:36:05,000
Qiumin has disappeared.

663
00:36:05,590 --> 00:36:06,190
Disappeared?

664
00:36:07,000 --> 00:36:07,590
What happened?

665
00:36:07,920 --> 00:36:08,960
News came from the Mirage Palace

666
00:36:09,320 --> 00:36:10,030
saying Qiumin took her people

667
00:36:10,070 --> 00:36:11,440
to clear the battlefield and then disappeared.

668
00:36:12,440 --> 00:36:13,190
Where could she have gone?

669
00:36:14,000 --> 00:36:14,760
Could something have happened to her?

670
00:36:28,880 --> 00:36:29,800
Miss Gao, you're awake.

671
00:36:31,880 --> 00:36:33,230
This is today's new tea.

672
00:36:34,030 --> 00:36:35,230
Come have a taste.

673
00:36:39,000 --> 00:36:40,030
Why am I here?

674
00:36:43,510 --> 00:36:44,760
That day at the Starfall Valley,

675
00:36:46,710 --> 00:36:48,510
