676
00:36:49,670 --> 00:36:51,000
Apart from the late Sang Qi

677
00:36:51,280 --> 00:36:52,000
and Madam Su,

678
00:36:52,550 --> 00:36:53,190
the others

679
00:36:53,920 --> 00:36:54,710
were Xuechen,

680
00:36:55,150 --> 00:36:55,800
Miss Mu,

681
00:36:57,030 --> 00:36:58,110
and you.

682
00:36:59,190 --> 00:37:00,070
In this great battle,

683
00:37:00,760 --> 00:37:02,030
He Xianwo vanished without a trace.

684
00:37:02,550 --> 00:37:03,880
But he has always desired the Chaos Pearl.

685
00:37:04,840 --> 00:37:06,360
He will undoubtedly hunt down those who know about it.

686
00:37:07,190 --> 00:37:08,230
And you

687
00:37:08,510 --> 00:37:09,550
