699
00:37:32,110 --> 00:37:33,410
We must use its power

700
00:37:33,410 --> 00:37:34,510
to rebuild the Immortals Array.

701
00:37:36,590 --> 00:37:38,320
Xie Xuechen will safeguard the Chaos Pearl.

702
00:37:39,000 --> 00:37:39,710
How to use it

703
00:37:40,150 --> 00:37:41,000
is his decision to make.

704
00:37:42,230 --> 00:37:43,070
Mr. Nan,

705
00:37:43,070 --> 00:37:44,320
