713
00:38:12,400 --> 00:38:13,740
You and Xie Xuechen

714
00:38:13,740 --> 00:38:14,840
are close friends.

715
00:38:15,400 --> 00:38:16,110
Shouldn't you

716
00:38:16,510 --> 00:38:17,710
