718
00:38:24,920 --> 00:38:27,320
I insist on hearing it

719
00:38:27,320 --> 00:38:28,150
from you?

720
00:38:29,030 --> 00:38:29,550
Mr. Nan,

721
00:38:29,550 --> 00:38:30,440
what are you trying to do?

722
00:38:31,280 --> 00:38:32,760
Are you afraid, Miss Gao?

723
00:38:33,000 --> 00:38:33,960
What is there for me to fear?

724
00:38:34,550 --> 00:38:35,280
Could it be

725
00:38:35,710 --> 00:38:37,190
you plan to harm me?

726
00:38:38,800 --> 00:38:40,070
You're joking.

727
00:38:41,440 --> 00:38:42,110
I simply wish

728
00:38:43,190 --> 00:38:45,400
to invite you to admire a painting.

729
00:38:47,150 --> 00:38:48,400
This painting of rivers and mountains

730
00:38:48,630 --> 00:38:50,150
was casually created by me.

731
00:38:50,840 --> 00:38:51,400
It features

732
00:38:51,710 --> 00:38:52,800
mountains, rivers,

733
00:38:53,030 --> 00:38:54,480
flowers, and birds...

734
00:38:55,280 --> 00:38:57,360
But it always feels like it's missing some soul.

735
00:38:59,670 --> 00:39:00,550
I'm uneducated and know nothing

736
00:39:00,800 --> 00:39:01,440
about appreciating paintings.

737
00:39:01,710 --> 00:39:02,550
I'll head back to the Mirage Palace now.

738
00:39:04,280 --> 00:39:05,510
Nan Xuyue, what are you trying to do?

739
00:39:08,920 --> 00:39:10,550
You seem rather anxious.

740
00:39:11,550 --> 00:39:12,840
Why not take another nap?

741
00:39:19,960 --> 00:39:21,070
Within the fan's realm,

742
00:39:22,110 --> 00:39:23,190
as a figure in the painting,

743
00:39:24,190 --> 00:39:25,710
this landscape and world

744
00:39:26,550 --> 00:39:28,030
are yours alone to enjoy.

745
00:39:29,880 --> 00:39:31,360
That should satisfy you.

746
00:39:48,360 --> 00:39:49,110
Mr. Nan,

747
00:39:49,110 --> 00:39:50,710
you seem rather unkind to a beauty.

748
00:39:51,150 --> 00:39:52,320
You overheard earlier.

749
00:39:53,590 --> 00:39:55,110
The Chaos Pearl is in Xie Xuechen's hands.

750
00:39:56,400 --> 00:39:57,630
But I'm curious.

751
00:39:59,230 --> 00:40:00,670
Sang Qi and Gao Qiumin

752
00:40:00,920 --> 00:40:02,150
stood on completely opposite sides,

753
00:40:02,630 --> 00:40:03,710
even as enemies.

754
00:40:04,760 --> 00:40:06,550
Yet they both tacitly remained silent.

755
00:40:07,800 --> 00:40:09,000
What exactly are they protecting?

756
00:40:09,920 --> 00:40:11,320
Is it the Chaos Pearl

757
00:40:12,280 --> 00:40:13,480
or someone else?

758
00:40:15,070 --> 00:40:16,150
Or could it be

759
00:40:17,400 --> 00:40:18,800
that the Chaos Pearl is this person?

760
00:40:21,920 --> 00:40:22,760
He Xianwo,

761
00:40:25,280 --> 00:40:26,440
give up your thoughts.

762
00:40:27,880 --> 00:40:28,670
I've told you,

763
00:40:29,880 --> 00:40:31,000
if you dare harm her,

764
00:40:32,440 --> 00:40:33,360
I'll destroy you.

765
00:40:35,070 --> 00:40:36,230
Don't you wish to visit

766
00:40:36,280 --> 00:40:37,230
the land of dreams?

767
00:40:37,480 --> 00:40:38,590
Between the one before me

768
00:40:39,030 --> 00:40:40,150
and the dreamland,

769
00:40:41,000 --> 00:40:42,590
if I cannot have both,

770
00:40:43,760 --> 00:40:44,840
I'll protect the former.

771
00:40:48,710 --> 00:40:49,960
Even if the one before you

772
00:40:50,440 --> 00:40:51,510
constantly disregards your feelings

773
00:40:51,550 --> 00:40:52,840
for Xie Xuechen's sake,

774
00:40:53,800 --> 00:40:55,150
and even blocks your plans?

775
00:41:15,110 --> 00:41:15,670
Indeed,

776
00:41:16,590 --> 00:41:17,630
it is excellent tea.

777
00:41:22,000 --> 00:41:24,110
The Chaos Pearl is the key to opening the Celestial Ladder.

778
00:41:24,550 --> 00:41:25,840
As long as the ladder is repaired,

779
00:41:26,710 --> 00:41:28,070
I can spare her life in the end.

780
00:41:29,920 --> 00:41:30,630
But Mr. Nan,

781
00:41:32,000 --> 00:41:32,710
don't tell me

782
00:41:33,510 --> 00:41:35,320
you can't bear to harm her even a little?

783
00:41:45,190 --> 00:41:47,510
What if I truly cannot bear it?

784
00:41:49,320 --> 00:41:51,150
Then why won't you kill Xie Xuechen?

785
00:41:52,920 --> 00:41:54,190
I've told you long ago,

786
00:41:54,800 --> 00:41:56,510
Xie Xuechen's existence is a threat.

787
00:41:57,480 --> 00:41:59,110
Not just to you and me,

788
00:41:59,440 --> 00:42:00,840
but also to Mu Xuanling.

789
00:42:01,360 --> 00:42:02,760
As long as Xie Xuechen lives,

790
00:42:02,960 --> 00:42:05,030
Mu Xuanling will continue

791
00:42:05,510 --> 00:42:06,960
