799
00:42:30,150 --> 00:42:30,920
Issue an Alliance Leader's decree.

800
00:42:31,320 --> 00:42:32,590
The entire Immortal Alliance is to hunt down He Xianwo.

801
00:42:32,800 --> 00:42:33,630
Not just a bounty,

802
00:42:34,000 --> 00:42:35,070
I'll provide a reward of ten thousand gold.

803
00:42:36,190 --> 00:42:36,590
No,

804
00:42:37,400 --> 00:42:38,110
no matter how much gold,

805
00:42:38,840 --> 00:42:39,960
I will find Qiumin.

806
00:42:52,840 --> 00:42:53,800
She'll be alright.

807
00:42:54,190 --> 00:42:55,000
Don't lose your focus.

808
00:42:56,590 --> 00:42:57,480
Lose my focus?

809
00:42:58,110 --> 00:42:59,590
