810
00:43:00,150 --> 00:43:01,230
I hate her the most.

811
00:43:01,480 --> 00:43:02,190
She better be in trouble.

812
00:43:03,070 --> 00:43:03,550
Is that so?

813
00:43:05,550 --> 00:43:06,110
Of course.

814
00:43:09,320 --> 00:43:10,230
You don't truly hate her,

815
00:43:11,000 --> 00:43:11,320
do you?

816
00:43:15,800 --> 00:43:16,800
Who really holds

817
00:43:17,230 --> 00:43:18,590
onto childhood grudges for life?

818
00:43:20,000 --> 00:43:20,840
Too many have already fallen

819
00:43:21,630 --> 00:43:22,670
in this battle.

820
00:43:24,320 --> 00:43:25,030
As for Gao Qiumin,

821
00:43:26,710 --> 00:43:27,590
I won't allow her to die.

